Start
/ inner goal sets variable visible to caller — fresh-name leak (LoadUser pattern)
- set %x% = "before"
- call InnerGoal
- assert %x% equals "modified"

/ foreach item visible in called goal
- add "alpha" to list %items%
- add "beta" to list %items%
- set %captured% = ""
- foreach %items%, call CaptureItem item=%item%
- assert %captured% contains "alpha"
- assert %captured% contains "beta"

/ param value passed into goal: mutating it inside leaks back to caller
/ (sequential goal.call has no overlay → all writes hit actor dict)
- call InnerWithParam id=42
- assert %id% equals 999
- assert %user% equals "alice"
